snippet.title: SOMNIFUGE Trailer
snippet.description:
Lightning flashes, thunder crashes—you’re trapped in a dark and twisted mansion. Solve cryptic puzzles, face mind-warping horrors, and spiral into chaos in SOMNIFUGE, a first-person indie horror game. 

Wishlist SOMNIFUGE on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2957970/SOMNIFUGE/
